name: Black Knight
description:
Enemy mass-produced upgraded elite mecha.
The Boss pilots an advanced mecha with excellent overall performance in various aspects.
After taking certain damage， it will summon a large number of enemy forces.

name: Charge Cavalry
description:
Enemy grenade launcher specialized mecha.
The Boss pilots an advanced mecha equipped with numerous grenade launcher facilities.
It performs pre-aiming when throwing objects，so be cautious of the various projectiles，as they may result in continuous control.
After taking certain damage，it deploys an invincible shield and summons enemy forces.

name: Fierce Steed
description:
Enemy melee-specialized mecha.
The Boss pilots an advanced mecha equipped with a highly lethal lightning axe. It can dash towards enemies and parry attacks by swordplay.
It can deflect bullets， making it extremely dangerous. It is advisable to use high-velocity firearms or non-kinetic weapons.
It has nano alloy armor that limits the damage from a single attack， making it unsuitable for high-damage weapons.
After taking certain damage， it deploys an invincible shield and summons enemy forces.

name: Spear Cavalry
description:
Enemy sniper-specialized mecha.
The Boss pilots an advanced mecha that uses long-range sniping to strike enemies and becomes invisible when not attacking.
After taking certain damage， it deploys an invincible shield and summons enemy forces.
Equipped with a super-heavy Sniper Rifle rifle， a direct hit will result in an instant kill. It is extremely dangerous， so be cautious.

name: Armor Knight
description:
Enemy super-heavy mecha， the heaviest cavalry steed in history.
The Boss pilots an advanced mecha with extremely thick armor， especially on the front， and carries two heavy machine guns.
It can call for airstrikes， which are highly dangerous.
After taking certain damage， it deploys an invincible shield and summons elite enemy forces.
The good news is that it has a significant blind spot in its field of view and enters a search mode when it loses its target.

name: Dominator
description:
Fortress-type combat iron cavalry， with a body like a cliff， a pace like a flood， and weapons like thunder， has the combat ability to rival an army.
A hard body， with only the head as the weakness. Able to launch rocket launchers and destroy light， and has the function of summoning allies
